<div style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 40px; background-color: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 8px;">
  <div style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 20px;">
    <h1 style="color: #e3342f;">Account Declined</h1>
  </div>

  <div style="font-size: 16px; color: #333;">
    <p>Dear <strong><%= @user.first_name %></strong>,</p>

    <p>
      Thank you for your interest in joining our platform. After carefully reviewing your account details, we regret to inform you that your registration has not been approved at this time.
    </p>

    <p>
      Please note this decision is based on our internal review policies. If you believe this was a mistake or would like to appeal the decision, feel free to contact our support team.
    </p>

    <p>
      We sincerely appreciate your time and understanding.
    </p>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
      Sincerely,<br>
      <strong>The Admin Team</strong>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
